						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/if-you-read-this-and-can-hear-me-new-poetry-by-fady-joudah/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">“If you read this and can hear me...” New Poetry by Fady Joudah</h7>
			</a>
			[…]

If you read this and can hear me,
what’s that smell? I, sour

before sweet, pugnacious
or placid, indentured
or...			
